## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-324">Le <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A> méthode doit être appelée à l’avance pour démarrer le processus de chargement.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-324">The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A> method must be called beforehand to start the loading process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-325">Il est possible de retourner un affichage avant que le chargeur de concepteur termine le chargement, car le concepteur racine, qui fournit l’affichage, est le premier objet créé par le chargeur de concepteur.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-325">It is possible to return a view before the designer loader finishes loading because the root designer, which supplies the view, is the first object created by the designer loader.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-326">Si une vue n’est pas disponible, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A> lève une exception.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-326">If a view is unavailable, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A> raises an exception.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-327">La notion d’une technologie d’affichage est obsolète.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-327">The notion of a view technology is obsolete.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-328">Toutefois, il reste dans les interfaces pour les concepteurs racine pour la compatibilité descendante.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-328">But, it remains in the interfaces for root designers for backward compatibility.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-329">Son utilisation est masquée à l’aide <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface> objets.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-329">Its use is hidden from anyone using <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-330">Le <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.View%2A> propriété masque les technologies d’affichage en passant les technologies prises en charge dans le concepteur racine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-330">The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.View%2A> property hides view technologies by passing the supported technologies back into the root designer.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f1ce0-331">Le code suivant montre l’exemple comment <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.View%2A> masque les technologies d’affichage.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f1ce0-331">The following code example shows how <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.View%2A> hides view technologies.</span></span>  

 ```csharp 
 IRootDesigner d;  

 ViewTechnology[] supported = d.SupportedTechnologies;  

 return d.GetView(supported[0]);
 ```
